Mexico’s President Enrique Pe<0xC3><0xB1>a Nieto is about to start his career.
As Mexico’s newly elected president Enrique Pe<0xC3><0xB1>a Nieto prepares to take office, BBC correspondent Will Grant invites us to look at the difficulties he will face and the mixed expectations of his country’s population.
The road traffic in Mexico is now in a particularly teary state.
